OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777551071
OL,3,CTwo men charged with the rape of a
OL,4,Cwoman
OL,6,FTwo men have appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fwith the rape of a woman in Plymouth.
OL,9,FHashmat Miakhel, aged 31, and Sayed
OL,10,FHoshmand, aged 19, appeared before
OL,11,FPlymouth Magistrates' Court on
OL,12,FTuesday, 28 April.
OL,14,FBoth men are accused of raping a woman
OL,15,Fat a residential property in the
OL,16,FSherford area of the city in the early
OL,17,Fhours of Sunday, 26 April.
OL,19,FBoth men, who are Afghan nationals,
OL,20,Fwere remanded in custody to appear at
OL,21,FPlymouth Crown Court in on June 1.
