OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777551071
OL,3,CTwo men charged with the rape of a
OL,4,Cwoman
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Katy Deer said:
OL,7,F"We understand the concern an incident
OL,8,Fsuch as this may cause, however, as
OL,9,Fcourt proceedings are now active, I
OL,10,Fask the public not to speculate and
OL,11,Frespect the legal process."
